1
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:35,940
♪Your secret, dangerous flaws♪

2
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:41,620
♪I can stay close
without seeing through♪

3
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:45,610
♪As long as it's about love♪

4
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:46,870
♪No matter how absurd♪

5
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:51,450
♪I choose to get used to it♪

6
00:00:52,810 --> 00:00:56,900
♪Truth or lies, you decide what's true♪

7
00:00:56,970 --> 00:01:00,800
♪I won't overturn it anymore♪

8
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,690
♪I cover my eyes and look♪

9
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:07,860
♪Is love an abyss or a trap♪

10
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:14,710
♪I only see the sparkle♪

11
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:37,980
=Turbulent Love=

12
00:01:38,060 --> 00:01:41,860
=Episode 19=
=Too Beautiful to Touch=

13
00:03:38,310 --> 00:03:39,150
Hao Yu.

14
00:03:40,630 --> 00:03:41,470
- Ji Zhijie...
- Hao Yu?

15
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,520
Ji Zhijie.

16
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:43,800
Hao Yu.

17
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,080
Hao Yu.

18
00:04:05,240 --> 00:04:06,080
Feihu?

19
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,710
Xiaocui?

20
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,920
You guys...

21
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,430
Why are you here?

22
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,400
Weren't you...

23
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,800
I'm fine, I'm fine.

24
00:04:14,190 --> 00:04:15,360
Mr. Ji saved me.

25
00:04:16,190 --> 00:04:17,160
You're safe now.

26
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,400
Don't you worry.

27
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,920
Zhijie had it all planned.

28
00:04:21,190 --> 00:04:22,030
We are all fine.

29
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:24,950
Zhijie did all this to earn
the trust of Councilman Zhu

30
00:04:25,270 --> 00:04:27,160
and Zhu Shuyi, so he could dismantle

31
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:28,560
the forces in Seronport.

32
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,870
He even had me fooled at first.

33
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:33,270
We grew up following Zhijie.

34
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:35,040
He's always been good to us.

35
00:04:35,870 --> 00:04:36,710
And for you, Yu...

36
00:04:37,190 --> 00:04:39,270
He'd never let a hair on your head be harmed.

37
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,510
That's why I found it so weird.

38
00:04:43,430 --> 00:04:44,680
On the day he drove me away,

39
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:46,950
I went back to see him.

40
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:07,960
Zhijie.

41
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:11,750
I told you to leave.

42
00:05:12,190 --> 00:05:13,120
Why are you back?

43
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,520
Go away!

44
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,080
I said go away!

45
00:05:26,310 --> 00:05:27,150
Zhijie,

46
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,950
I've been with you all these years.

47
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,950
Even if you're wrong,

48
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:33,830
I'll do as you say.

49
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,800
But driving me away?

50
00:05:37,160 --> 00:05:38,000
I can't do it.

51
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,320
Hit me.

52
00:05:49,630 --> 00:05:50,470
Beat me to death.

53
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:52,160
Just take my life.

54
00:05:54,190 --> 00:05:55,160
There's no one else here.

55
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,750
Please tell me the truth.

56
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,160
I've said all I need to say.

57
00:06:06,310 --> 00:06:07,430
Don't you get it?

58
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,800
I'm not like Feihu or Feiying.

59
00:06:12,950 --> 00:06:13,800
Even if I have to go,

60
00:06:15,430 --> 00:06:16,600
or if I die,

61
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,560
I want to die knowing the truth.

62
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,950
Feiying, Feihu,

63
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,560
and Xiaocui

64
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,190
are all alive.

65
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:27,310
I'll have someone pull you out of the water.

66
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,320
Don't be afraid.

67
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:30,680
From now on,

68
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,680
just follow my lead.

69
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,390
I'd save you for Hao Yu's sake anyway.

70
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:52,680
Why are you crying?

71
00:08:02,310 --> 00:08:04,040
So that's why you did it, Zhijie.

72
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,190
Now I understand.

73
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:08,910
Zhijie,

74
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:11,190
you're quite the actor.

75
00:08:20,310 --> 00:08:22,240
We were forced to join Cangfeng.

76
00:08:23,390 --> 00:08:24,270
We've done the dirty work,

77
00:08:25,070 --> 00:08:25,950
shed blood and taken lives.

78
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,950
But now, I want to do something right.

79
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,480
We've nearly died several times.

80
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,080
You saved us every time.

81
00:08:37,550 --> 00:08:38,390
My life

82
00:08:39,030 --> 00:08:39,870
is yours to take.

83
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,750
But please don't drive us away.

84
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:46,480
Same here.

85
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,440
Same here.

86
00:09:04,240 --> 00:09:05,960
Why did Ji Zhijie do this?

87
00:09:06,670 --> 00:09:07,960
Why didn't he say anything?

88
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,200
Where is he now?

89
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:12,630
Yu.

90
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,390
Since you started hurting yourself,

91
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,680
Zhijie has been

92
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,150
drowning in guilt.

93
00:10:03,790 --> 00:10:04,630
Hao Yu.

94
00:10:06,150 --> 00:10:06,990
Hao Yu!

95
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,550
The doctor said it was luckily found early.

96
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,080
The cut isn't deep.

97
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,840
(Does loving me)

98
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,910
(make you feel like dying?)

99
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:54,080
♪Suddenly the sky turns dark♪

100
00:10:54,330 --> 00:10:59,640
♪The rain of love is pouring down heavily♪

101
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:05,050
♪Before fate is washed away♪

102
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:09,020
♪My soul's been flooded♪

103
00:11:11,270 --> 00:11:12,320
One of you is human,

104
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:13,600
the other is a monster.

105
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:15,360
We are from two different worlds.

106
00:11:15,670 --> 00:11:17,320
Even if you're willing to crawl

107
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:19,910
out of hell in human skin for her sake-

108
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:21,960
Too many lies stood in our way-

109
00:11:22,120 --> 00:11:23,630
Suspicion, and hatred.

110
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,040
Your lives

111
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:28,080
aren't yours to decide.

112
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:31,870
Even if you tore out
your heart to give to her,

113
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:34,720
she wouldn't accept it.

114
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,600
From the very beginning,

115
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:39,790
you were wrong.

116
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,750
Dead wrong!

117
00:11:42,790 --> 00:11:44,320
When I adopted you,

118
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,150
I meant to raise you

119
00:11:46,510 --> 00:11:48,000
as my successor.

120
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,960
But everything went wrong.

121
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:51,910
Love isn't forcing,

122
00:11:53,440 --> 00:11:55,360
controlling, or possessing.

123
00:11:56,030 --> 00:11:57,240
Love is about respect

124
00:11:58,550 --> 00:11:59,630
and fulfillment.

125
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:02,240
What do you want me to fulfill?

126
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:03,350
Hao Yu?

127
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,440
What do you want?

128
00:12:06,510 --> 00:12:07,750
Turn myself in right now,

129
00:12:08,240 --> 00:12:10,080
let you kill me right here,

130
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:13,270
or wipe out all of the forces

131
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,840
in Cangfeng and Seronport?

132
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:17,440
Will that make you happy?

133
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:18,390
Will it?

134
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,630
But you won't do that.

135
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:24,870
(I will.)

136
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:26,870
(I will do that,)

137
00:12:28,150 --> 00:12:29,320
(but not just yet.)

138
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:32,750
(I'm going to clear)

139
00:12:32,750 --> 00:12:34,600
(this treacherous path for you.)

140
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,480
(Since I love you,)

141
00:12:37,910 --> 00:12:39,240
(I won't tie you down.)

142
00:12:39,750 --> 00:12:40,750
(I want you to be happy.)

143
00:12:40,750 --> 00:12:42,100
♪Love took...♪

144
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,120
(So whatever you want to do,)

145
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,240
(whatever justice you're after,)

146
00:12:47,150 --> 00:12:48,870
(I'll get it back for you with my own hands.)

147
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:53,680
(Hao Yu,)

148
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,790
(wake up.)

149
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,320
(You have to live on to hate me.)

150
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:03,970
♪Entangled with you♪

151
00:13:04,110 --> 00:13:08,040
♪Let me stay in your rainy days♪

152
00:13:08,230 --> 00:13:12,120
♪Unaware of the changing seasons♪

153
00:13:12,310 --> 00:13:14,900
♪With eyes closed♪

154
00:13:15,110 --> 00:13:18,960
♪Your hate or lies♪

155
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:26,000
♪I take it all as love♪

156
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,200
Eat.

157
00:13:56,750 --> 00:13:57,750
Ji Zhijie, what do you want?

158
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,480
If you leave even a grain of rice,

159
00:13:59,670 --> 00:14:00,510
I'll dump it.

160
00:14:00,790 --> 00:14:02,000
If you hurt yourself again,

161
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,150
I'll make all of Seronport

162
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:04,510
taste what it feels like.

163
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:05,630
Ji Zhijie, you're crazy!

164
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:06,670
I gave you a chance.

165
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,200
Eat.

166
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:15,390
Since you'd rather choose death over me,

167
00:15:16,840 --> 00:15:18,720
I'm done treating you like a fragile prize.

168
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:22,440
You're not going to the UK.

169
00:15:24,080 --> 00:15:26,200
I won't indulge or spoil you anymore.

170
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:30,120
Hao Yu, I want you to live and pay

171
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,270
for what you've done.

172
00:15:34,790 --> 00:15:36,120
But I promise,

173
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,870
if you behave yourself and eat properly,

174
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:47,320
I'll let you go.

175
00:15:58,670 --> 00:15:59,510
(I'm sorry.)

176
00:16:01,270 --> 00:16:02,110
(I'm sorry.)

177
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:03,590
(I'm sorry.)

178
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:07,270
(If hate is what keeps you alive,)

179
00:16:08,030 --> 00:16:09,030
(then hate me.)

180
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:11,270
(Keep hating me,)

181
00:16:11,640 --> 00:16:12,480
(pull yourself together,)

182
00:16:12,510 --> 00:16:14,440
(do whatever it takes
to take me down, and kill me.)

183
00:16:15,550 --> 00:16:16,390
(Besides,)

184
00:16:17,550 --> 00:16:19,000
(even if you look me with such loathing,)

185
00:16:20,910 --> 00:16:23,120
(I want that gaze to
linger on me a little longer.)

186
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:27,510
Tell Councilman Zhu

187
00:16:27,510 --> 00:16:28,480
I accept his gifts.

188
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:31,000
Round up the guys. Ancestral hall. Now.

189
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:32,470
Zhijie.

190
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:34,270
Have you made up your mind?

191
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:44,750
Feilong.

192
00:16:45,750 --> 00:16:47,320
I need to see someone first.

193
00:16:48,440 --> 00:16:49,280
Okay.

194
00:17:02,270 --> 00:17:03,480
You wanted to see me?

195
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,310
That's a surprise.

196
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:09,440
I've gone through all your police files.

197
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,960
You're the cleanest cop and the most

198
00:17:13,110 --> 00:17:13,960
upright one.

199
00:17:16,310 --> 00:17:17,240
I want to work with you.

200
00:17:19,110 --> 00:17:20,270
I will help you dismantle

201
00:17:20,270 --> 00:17:21,680
every syndicate in Seronport.

202
00:17:23,720 --> 00:17:24,560
Including you?

203
00:17:27,510 --> 00:17:28,350
Including me,

204
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,280
and Cangfeng.

205
00:17:35,550 --> 00:17:36,720
But I have a few conditions.

206
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:38,960
My guys

207
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:40,480
were forced into Cangfeng.

208
00:17:41,510 --> 00:17:42,790
Some don't deserve to die.

209
00:17:43,480 --> 00:17:45,200
If the law allows,

210
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,720
I want their sentences reduced.

211
00:17:48,750 --> 00:17:49,880
Give them a chance to start over

212
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,320
and go straight.

213
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:53,560
You have my word.

214
00:17:54,110 --> 00:17:54,950
Anything else?

215
00:17:57,350 --> 00:17:59,270
She has been your source.

216
00:18:01,640 --> 00:18:02,830
Whatever happens,

217
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:04,830
you must make sure

218
00:18:04,830 --> 00:18:06,350
she's safe and free.

219
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:08,870
Don't worry.

220
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,880
My duty is to protect every citizen

221
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:13,430
in Seronport.

222
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,000
One more thing.

223
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:24,480
To make her eat,

224
00:18:25,400 --> 00:18:26,750
I've done something highly disrespectful.

225
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:28,960
I hope you can go see her.

226
00:18:29,270 --> 00:18:30,200
Help her pull it together.

227
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:32,750
Make her believe there is

228
00:18:32,750 --> 00:18:33,960
still hope and good cops

229
00:18:34,920 --> 00:18:35,830
left in this world.

230
00:18:41,070 --> 00:18:41,910
Ji Zhijie,

231
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:44,680
you're just like the rumors-

232
00:18:46,510 --> 00:18:47,350
brave, resourceful,

233
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:50,160
and a hopeless romantic.

234
00:18:58,270 --> 00:18:59,680
I'm not a big hero.

235
00:19:01,160 --> 00:19:02,640
I don't have your grand ambitions.

236
00:19:12,180 --> 00:19:19,220
(Guan Renjie)

237
00:19:27,400 --> 00:19:28,310
I won't give up.

238
00:19:29,310 --> 00:19:30,240
You shouldn't either!

239
00:19:30,750 --> 00:19:32,510
Officer Guan wouldn't want you to give up!

240
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,480
Walk me through

241
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:39,520
your plan.

242
00:19:44,880 --> 00:19:45,790
I'm going all in

243
00:19:47,110 --> 00:19:48,110
to become the kingpin.

244
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:13,030
(If falling into a darker world)

245
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:14,270
(can buy your path to the light,)

246
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:17,640
(then I'll stay)

247
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:19,000
(in the abyss forever.)

248
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:24,440
- (Playing along with hypocrites)
- A pleasure.

249
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:25,830
(isn't hard at all.)

250
00:20:26,590 --> 00:20:27,440
- (What's hard is)
- Cheers.

251
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,280
Cheers.

252
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:30,200
(facing the people who care about you)

253
00:20:31,590 --> 00:20:32,920
(and lying to their faces.)

254
00:20:33,200 --> 00:20:34,240
Who told you to do that?

255
00:20:35,200 --> 00:20:36,310
Got guts now, huh?

256
00:20:37,030 --> 00:20:38,030
- Who told you to do that?
- Zhijie.

257
00:20:38,310 --> 00:20:39,150
Zhijie...

258
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:41,790
Come on, Feiying. Are you a model citizen?

259
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:44,200
Never done a dirty deed in your life?

260
00:20:44,440 --> 00:20:45,790
And now you're lecturing me on morality?

261
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,040
Who taught you that?

262
00:20:48,270 --> 00:20:49,110
Who taught you that?

263
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,590
- You!
- Zhijie.

264
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,440
Drag him to the kennel.

265
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:55,030
Then send him to Councilman Zhu

266
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:56,550
to kneel for forgiveness.

267
00:20:57,030 --> 00:20:58,790
Don't come back until he's satisfied.

268
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:00,280
Zhijie!

269
00:21:00,440 --> 00:21:01,920
I'm still your boss anyway.

270
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,070
Don't think I don't know

271
00:21:04,070 --> 00:21:05,030
Lianxing offered you

272
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,200
a truckload of gold,

273
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,750
and now you dare talk to me like this.

274
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:09,160
If you want out,

275
00:21:09,160 --> 00:21:10,590
get out right now!

276
00:21:13,200 --> 00:21:14,350
They did offer it to me,

277
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:16,750
but I didn't take a single piece.

278
00:21:18,550 --> 00:21:20,480
Don't believe rumors and turn against us.

279
00:21:22,270 --> 00:21:23,640
I do have my suspicions.

280
00:21:23,720 --> 00:21:24,720
Let me tell you, Feilong.

281
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:26,510
All good things come to an end.

282
00:21:26,830 --> 00:21:27,670
Go.

283
00:21:27,880 --> 00:21:28,720
You.

284
00:21:29,110 --> 00:21:29,950
And you.

285
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:31,720
All of you, go.

286
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:33,800
Go abroad.

287
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,510
Go to Xingzhou Port.

288
00:21:35,880 --> 00:21:37,110
Get out of Seronport.

289
00:21:37,640 --> 00:21:39,000
From today on,

290
00:21:39,830 --> 00:21:42,270
I won't tolerate a single whiff of betrayal.

291
00:21:44,030 --> 00:21:45,750
This isn't like you at all.

292
00:21:46,550 --> 00:21:47,830
If you have a plan or a problem,

293
00:21:48,830 --> 00:21:50,000
please just tell us.

294
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,680
Didn't I make myself clear?

295
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:53,720
This is exactly what I want!

296
00:21:54,960 --> 00:21:55,960
All of you, get out!

297
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:07,480
Fine.

298
00:22:08,920 --> 00:22:09,760
Zhijie,

299
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:11,350
you want us to leave,

300
00:22:13,550 --> 00:22:14,590
but I, Feilong,

301
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:17,590
won't leave Ji Zhijie and Cangfeng!

302
00:22:29,200 --> 00:22:31,110
(And the hardest part of all this-)

303
00:22:31,270 --> 00:22:32,680
Hao Yu, stop flattering yourself.

304
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:33,520
(is facing you.)

305
00:22:33,530 --> 00:22:34,400
Get this straight.

306
00:22:35,310 --> 00:22:36,960
The only reason I'm keeping you alive

307
00:22:37,240 --> 00:22:38,830
is to torture you

308
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:41,270
and make you pay.

309
00:22:44,280 --> 00:22:46,480
You'd better stay home
and keep out of trouble.

310
00:22:47,350 --> 00:22:49,030
The more you try to bring me down,

311
00:22:49,830 --> 00:22:50,790
the more you'll see

312
00:22:50,790 --> 00:22:52,830
I'm untouchable.

313
00:24:09,830 --> 00:24:10,710
Miss Hao!

314
00:24:10,760 --> 00:24:11,630
Please save me!

315
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:12,720
- What are you doing?
- Save me!

316
00:24:12,830 --> 00:24:13,880
- Save me
- Get up.

317
00:24:14,480 --> 00:24:15,350
What happened to you?

318
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,040
Feihu,

319
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:20,200
Ji Zhijie took over Li Island
to build a factory

320
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,920
and turned a lounge into a marketplace.

321
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:25,350
He made me transfer it to Zhu Shuyi

322
00:24:25,590 --> 00:24:26,960
just to run this shady business?

323
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:28,960
No, no, no.

324
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,350
There must be some misunderstanding.

325
00:24:31,560 --> 00:24:32,420
(You're so smart.)

326
00:24:32,430 --> 00:24:33,590
(You must know what I'm doing.)

327
00:24:34,440 --> 00:24:35,550
(Your sense of justice will)

328
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:37,110
(definitely make you step in.)

329
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:40,070
(But to earn the trust)

330
00:24:40,070 --> 00:24:41,510
(of the Councilman and Zhu Shuyi,)

331
00:24:42,310 --> 00:24:44,310
- (I must keep playing the tyrant)
- You...

332
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:45,590
(and be cruel to you.)

333
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:47,480
(Only this way)

334
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,960
(can I clear you of this completely.)

335
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,720
- M-My face...
- I'm sorry.

336
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:52,640
- Sorry.
- My hair!

337
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:54,160
I'm so sorry, Miss Zhu.

338
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,280
I'm sorry.

339
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:58,160
Miss Zhu and I have some unfinished business.

340
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:00,790
I'll apologize to Miss Zhu.

341
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,350
I'll beg for her forgiveness, okay?

342
00:25:18,350 --> 00:25:19,400
Keep kneeling if you want.

343
00:25:25,200 --> 00:25:26,040
In the past,

344
00:25:26,040 --> 00:25:27,160
- (It's going to rain.)
- Zhong Jiali told me

345
00:25:27,160 --> 00:25:28,200
you were a hopeless romantic.

346
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:31,030
- (I must get Zhu Shuyi in soon.)
- But you don't

347
00:25:31,030 --> 00:25:33,000
come across that way.

348
00:25:36,960 --> 00:25:38,200
People change.

349
00:25:40,920 --> 00:25:42,070
Earlier,

350
00:25:42,830 --> 00:25:44,510
the sea breeze felt nice.

351
00:25:46,310 --> 00:25:48,000
But now it's all dark clouds

352
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:49,200
and lightning out there.

353
00:26:04,640 --> 00:26:05,480
Miss Zhu,

354
00:26:07,550 --> 00:26:09,030
what I want now

355
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:12,440
is money, power, and status-

356
00:26:12,830 --> 00:26:13,670
more than

357
00:26:14,030 --> 00:26:14,870
Liang Zhaokun ever had.

358
00:26:15,790 --> 00:26:16,920
You've been good to me.

359
00:26:17,790 --> 00:26:18,830
I'd say you are the perfect

360
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,640
candidate for a marriage alliance.

361
00:26:21,720 --> 00:26:22,640
Right now,

362
00:26:23,030 --> 00:26:25,720
you're the one I approve of the most.

363
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,040
Tomorrow,

364
00:26:33,070 --> 00:26:35,680
I'll take you to meet the insiders.

365
00:26:37,720 --> 00:26:39,400
And we'll tell them

366
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:40,960
about our marriage.

367
00:26:55,750 --> 00:26:56,720
It looks like

368
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,640
I'll have to stay

369
00:26:58,830 --> 00:27:00,110
at your place tonight.

370
00:27:00,350 --> 00:27:01,880
Those reporters haven't left yet.

371
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:04,350
Stay as long as you like.

372
00:27:08,270 --> 00:27:09,110
So,

373
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:10,720
which room is mine?

374
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:13,270
Whichever you want.

375
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:20,510
It's going to rain.

376
00:27:23,350 --> 00:27:25,590
Miss Zhu, you're so eager to marry me.

377
00:27:26,510 --> 00:27:29,000
Do you expect me to
clean up the Councilman's mess?

378
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:32,240
Mr. Ji,

379
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:34,310
you'll have twice the leverage.

380
00:27:34,510 --> 00:27:35,590
Buy one, get one free.

381
00:27:37,240 --> 00:27:38,350
From now on,

382
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:41,880
these will be your key assets in the game.

383
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:44,680
The more blame you take for Godfather,

384
00:27:44,960 --> 00:27:46,790
the more rewards he will give you.

385
00:27:47,160 --> 00:27:48,240
Your position

386
00:27:48,640 --> 00:27:49,830
will only keep rising.

387
00:27:52,350 --> 00:27:53,190
I understand.

388
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:55,520
I understand.

389
00:27:56,350 --> 00:27:57,750
I hope this is a good idea.

390
00:27:58,310 --> 00:28:00,400
So, tonight...

391
00:28:00,550 --> 00:28:02,000
Miss Zhu, you should get some rest.

392
00:28:02,720 --> 00:28:03,680
I'll leave you be.

393
00:28:04,550 --> 00:28:05,390
I'll sleep in the study.

394
00:28:36,750 --> 00:28:38,270
Give her an umbrella and bring her in.

395
00:28:38,440 --> 00:28:39,880
Tell her she's wasting her time.

396
00:28:40,440 --> 00:28:41,350
Say it the way I taught you.

397
00:28:42,110 --> 00:28:42,950
Go.

398
00:28:50,040 --> 00:28:51,260
Miss Hao, it's raining.

399
00:28:51,270 --> 00:28:52,440
Get up and come inside.

400
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:54,590
I told you to check on Feihu.

401
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:55,590
How are they doing?

402
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:57,550
I just came from the kennel.

403
00:28:57,790 --> 00:28:58,630
Feihu...

404
00:28:58,750 --> 00:29:00,110
He's barely recognizable.

405
00:29:00,510 --> 00:29:02,070
But luckily, Feilong arrived in time

406
00:29:02,070 --> 00:29:03,110
and sent him to the hospital.

407
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:05,350
He said he doesn't blame you

408
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:06,830
and you shouldn't blame yourself.

409
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:08,500
He also said

410
00:29:08,510 --> 00:29:10,750
although he doesn't know as much as Feilong

411
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:12,880
about what happened between you and Zhijie,

412
00:29:13,590 --> 00:29:15,030
he wants you to take care of yourself.

413
00:29:15,030 --> 00:29:16,830
He'll never see you any differently.

414
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:18,080
And if you

415
00:29:18,310 --> 00:29:19,680
really can't hold on anymore,

416
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:20,630
just leave.

417
00:29:20,750 --> 00:29:21,630
Because Zhijie

418
00:29:21,680 --> 00:29:23,110
is not the same as before.

419
00:29:23,750 --> 00:29:24,590
I'll talk to him.

420
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:25,750
- Ji Zhijie!
- It won't work, Miss Hao.

421
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:27,390
- Ji Zhijie!
- It won't work!

422
00:29:30,270 --> 00:29:31,110
It won't work.

423
00:29:31,510 --> 00:29:32,750
I heard him on the phone.

424
00:29:33,070 --> 00:29:33,920
That waitress's eyes

425
00:29:34,270 --> 00:29:35,480
have been gouged out.

426
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:39,920
It's true, Miss Hao.

427
00:29:40,750 --> 00:29:42,350
They took videos and photos

428
00:29:42,680 --> 00:29:45,240
for Mr. Ji and Miss Zhu to confirm.

429
00:29:54,960 --> 00:29:55,800
Get up.

430
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,190
Get up.

431
00:30:38,880 --> 00:30:40,510
You're all thumbs.
You can't do anything right.

432
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:42,760
After tonight...

433
00:30:43,830 --> 00:30:44,670
Right,

434
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:47,560
tonight is the night.

435
00:30:49,110 --> 00:30:50,110
As long as you behave

436
00:30:50,160 --> 00:30:51,310
and stay in line,

437
00:30:53,070 --> 00:30:54,110
I can let you go.

438
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,590
You will be free.

439
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,590
(I can't stand treating you)

440
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:07,830
(like this even for a single day.)

441
00:31:09,200 --> 00:31:10,200
(I want to hold your hand.)

442
00:31:11,440 --> 00:31:12,510
(I want you to hug me.)

443
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:14,830
(I want to hug you too.)

444
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,830
(But I can't drop)

445
00:31:19,030 --> 00:31:20,880
(this charade now.)

446
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:38,000
You have a fever.

447
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:41,830
Don't you hate me?

448
00:31:43,480 --> 00:31:44,320
Just go away.

449
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,070
Go!

450
00:31:51,920 --> 00:31:52,880
(I don't want to let you go.)

451
00:31:53,960 --> 00:31:54,800
(But...)

452
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:58,270
(I have no choice.)

453
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:00,800
Go!

454
00:32:04,270 --> 00:32:05,200
Go!

455
00:32:07,030 --> 00:32:08,200
All of you, go!

456
00:32:10,070 --> 00:32:11,240
Go away.

457
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:16,270
(I have to wait)

458
00:32:16,270 --> 00:32:18,350
(until the day I gain their full trust.)

459
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:22,000
(Only then can I safely send you away.)

460
00:32:36,200 --> 00:32:37,040
Cheers.

461
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,000
If you want in,

462
00:32:42,640 --> 00:32:44,000
you need to prove yourself.

463
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,070
If you can't deal with her,

464
00:32:46,550 --> 00:32:47,480
we'll do it for you.

465
00:32:53,790 --> 00:32:55,200
She's no threat.

466
00:32:56,550 --> 00:32:57,880
Don't waste your breath on her.

467
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:03,480
I raise this glass

468
00:33:04,750 --> 00:33:06,310
to the big picture.

469
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:16,680
Smart boy.

470
00:33:17,110 --> 00:33:17,950
Cheers.

471
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:20,350
To the big picture.

472
00:33:20,550 --> 00:33:21,390
Cheers.

473
00:33:26,790 --> 00:33:28,000
Come on, dig in.

474
00:33:28,200 --> 00:33:29,040
Come on.

475
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:40,830
(They are threating you.)

476
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:43,880
(You're putting yourself at risk.)

477
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:47,640
(The safest way)

478
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,480
(is to make you disappear)

479
00:33:51,070 --> 00:33:53,510
(and remove you from the plan completely.)

480
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,960
You set this up.

481
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,670
After Guan Renjie died,

482
00:34:18,630 --> 00:34:19,800
Zhou Ziheng showed up.

483
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:21,800
After a reporter died,

484
00:34:21,920 --> 00:34:23,510
random cops showed up.

485
00:34:23,510 --> 00:34:25,400
You're the one who deserves to die!

486
00:34:42,190 --> 00:34:43,480
I'm done protecting her.

487
00:34:44,960 --> 00:34:46,000
Do whatever you want.

488
00:34:54,920 --> 00:34:55,760
(Alright.)

489
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:58,000
(It's all over.)

490
00:34:59,480 --> 00:35:01,030
(Everything is over.)

491
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:56,800
Hello?

492
00:35:57,710 --> 00:35:59,320
The new product launch today.

493
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:00,760
Are you all set?

494
00:36:01,710 --> 00:36:02,550
Yes.

495
00:36:03,920 --> 00:36:06,280
All the key figures will be there today.

496
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:07,320
This time,

497
00:36:07,360 --> 00:36:09,030
we must make sure nothing goes wrong.

498
00:36:09,480 --> 00:36:10,320
Sure.

499
00:36:44,150 --> 00:36:44,990
(Hao Yu,)

500
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:47,190
(it's finally coming to an end.)

501
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:54,570
♪Don't take amber from my eyes♪

502
00:36:56,450 --> 00:37:00,570
♪I'm scared you'll be swallowed by dark♪

503
00:37:02,010 --> 00:37:04,330
♪Watching you get tied down♪

504
00:37:04,330 --> 00:37:06,430
♪Trapped in the corner♪

505
00:37:06,470 --> 00:37:08,940
♪My heart feels torn apart♪

506
00:37:09,250 --> 00:37:14,570
♪Even if it's an abyss, I'll fall♪

507
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:19,820
♪Gray fireworks♪

508
00:37:20,060 --> 00:37:23,150
♪Pushing back the bright corners♪

509
00:37:23,570 --> 00:37:26,700
♪Waiting for you to wake up♪

510
00:37:26,700 --> 00:37:30,440
♪Hurts me too much♪

511
00:37:30,630 --> 00:37:33,920
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

512
00:37:33,920 --> 00:37:37,670
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

513
00:37:38,100 --> 00:37:40,430
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

514
00:37:40,600 --> 00:37:44,890
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

515
00:37:45,090 --> 00:37:48,260
♪Don't leave me to survive alone♪

516
00:37:48,260 --> 00:37:52,170
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

517
00:37:52,630 --> 00:37:58,490
♪I pray and confess through pain♪

518
00:38:01,040 --> 00:38:03,960
♪I learned to let go of myself♪

519
00:38:04,710 --> 00:38:07,480
♪I burn away every bitter result♪

520
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:09,070
♪Just to light♪

521
00:38:09,240 --> 00:38:13,240
♪Eternal fireworks for you♪

522
00:38:13,790 --> 00:38:16,930
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

523
00:38:16,930 --> 00:38:20,740
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

524
00:38:21,120 --> 00:38:23,450
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

525
00:38:23,600 --> 00:38:27,880
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

526
00:38:28,070 --> 00:38:31,220
♪Don't leave me to survive alone♪

527
00:38:31,220 --> 00:38:35,240
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

